comments.body:
There are a total of 77,515 bibs that are likely mistakes from the P2E file. Of those, 9,031 only have URLs for tables of contents from the Library of Congress. I will work with Enterprise Services to experiment in the Alma sandbox to find a way to remove the portfolios from these records.

To be clear, the URLs themselves won't be removed from the records. They will just have the portfolios removed.
Thank you @mzelesky !
